DESCRIPTION

This file contains an overview of the contents of the mpeg2_streamit_codec bundle.

CONTENTS

DCT_IEEE - readme information for the DCT files
MPEG2 - readme information for the MPEG2 files
INSTALL - installation instructions
docs/ - StreamIt docs for all the StreamIt files
streamit/ - Source code for the MPEG2 codec
input/ - Sample input files for running the MPEG2 decoder and encoder
